reviewText:
The grand finale arrives, and nothing less than the fate of the world is at stake!  But the path to victory is long, and Ryuuko starts in a very low place, and only her friends and bitterest enemies can save her!  Alliances will be tested, tears and blood will be shed, hearts will be lifted, and more people will get naked!  And don't forget the bonus episode afterward!

See this and remember why you love anime so much!
This product is exquisite. I would totally buy from this seller again
